{"thag4.11:0.1":"Theragatha 4.11 ","thag4.11:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","thag4.11:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag4.11:0.4":"Sappakattheragatha ","thag4.11:1.1":"“Yada balaka sucipandaracchada, ","thag4.11:1.2":"Kalassa meghassa bhayena tajjita; ","thag4.11:1.3":"Palehiti alayamalayesini, ","thag4.11:1.4":"Tada nadi ajakarani rameti mam. ","thag4.11:2.1":"Yada balaka suvisuddhapandara, ","thag4.11:2.2":"Kalassa meghassa bhayena tajjita; ","thag4.11:2.3":"Pariyesati lenamalenadassini, ","thag4.11:2.4":"Tada nadi ajakarani rameti mam. ","thag4.11:3.1":"Kam nu tattha na ramenti, ","thag4.11:3.2":"jambuyo ubhato tahim; ","thag4.11:3.3":"Sobhenti apagakulam, ","thag4.11:3.4":"mama lenassa pacchato. ","thag4.11:4.1":"Tamatamadasanghasuppahina, ","thag4.11:4.2":"Bheka mandavati panadayanti; ","thag4.11:4.3":"‘Najja girinadihi vippavasasamayo, ","thag4.11:4.4":"Khema ajakarani siva suramma’”ti. ","thag4.11:4.5":"… Sappako thero …. "}